  "detailed_description": "<h1>关注我们：</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>新浪微博：游戏逻辑<br><br></li><li>官方QQ群：  258788848<br><br>感谢大家的关注。</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>我一直在等，等祂来接我，<br>如今祂终于来了，<br>你看，他们都在这艘黑船之上！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079950/extras/b7f91c8874f66608a4f64ab88c3085d7.avif?t=1718166846\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br>可那人一直找寻的“慈航”终将驶向哪里？或许这一切的因由，唯有“无者”才能解答。<br><br>深入亡者怨念产生的“怨秽地”，解开深渊中的谜团，探索隐藏在人们内心深处的真实往事。<br><br><strong><i>除此之外，也许......你还可以改变些什么......</i></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2>《残秽的我们2》是一款本土原创写实插画风的恐怖冒险游戏，游戏风格主打的中式惊悚恐怖，游戏内不仅含有大量佛教与东方元素，还有那些骇人听闻的习俗、以及曾经鲜活的生活在这世上的人们。<br><br><br><strong>这一次“怨秽地”中还潜伏着更恐怖的东西。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079950/extras/48818a7473de7390481f1f842f9ff104.poster.avif?t=1718166846\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079950/extras/48818a7473de7390481f1f842f9ff104.webm?t=1718166846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079950/extras/48818a7473de7390481f1f842f9ff104.mp4?t=1718166846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索</h2>跟随女主“无者”的脚步，踏入那艘名为“慈航”的黑船，一步一步揭开隐藏其中的真相。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079950/extras/954e029503fa7a7e5ba21f6438a535ca.poster.avif?t=1718166846\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079950/extras/954e029503fa7a7e5ba21f6438a535ca.webm?t=1718166846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079950/extras/954e029503fa7a7e5ba21f6438a535ca.mp4?t=1718166846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多角色</h2>除“无者”外，还可以交替操作事件中其他几位角色，通过不同的视角去还原那场悲剧背后的真相。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079950/extras/550720947578e885d8b946470de2a412.poster.avif?t=1718166846\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079950/extras/550720947578e885d8b946470de2a412.webm?t=1718166846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079950/extras/550720947578e885d8b946470de2a412.mp4?t=1718166846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法</h2>浓郁的本土文化色彩，体验偏远城镇中的奇闻异事。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079950/extras/dcc974b82d7ab7806663ea008409f8cd.poster.avif?t=1718166846\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079950/extras/dcc974b82d7ab7806663ea008409f8cd.webm?t=1718166846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079950/extras/dcc974b82d7ab7806663ea008409f8cd.mp4?t=1718166846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >提升</h2>※<strong>音乐</strong>：每个人物的专属的BGM，都恰如其分的展现出了属于他们自己的性格和命运。<br>※<strong>佛乐</strong>：将佛经与各种风格迥异的音乐相融，每个场景、每尊菩萨都深含着丰富的寓意。<br>※<strong>画面</strong>：不再局限于传统2D游戏画面与转场方式，大量采用了电影化的镜头语言表达，提升玩家的游玩感受。<br>※<strong>故事</strong>：不仅有着更加饱满的故事，在那座小镇之中，还有隐藏着许多秘密等你去发现。</li></ul>",
